# gooshtkub = thickness/length*breadth  kam bashad
case=mobile %>% filter(company=="Nokia")
gooshtkubiat=case$dim_thickness/(case$dim_length*case$dim_breadth)

  group_by(device) %>% 
  summarise(gooshtkubiat=dim_thickness/(dim_length*dim_breadth),year=year) %>% arrange(desc(gooshtkubiat))  ->stat
